    KRBP -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>localhost (no encryption)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User<br/>x-forwarded-access-token"| Fastify

    %% Module federation (internal pod)
    Fastify -->|"HTTPS/8043<br/>TLS (service-ca)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token"| ModelReg
