    Fastify -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>No encryption<br/>User token"| Perses
    Fastify -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS<br/>User token"| MLflow
    Fastify -->|"HTTPS/9092<br/>TLS<br/>SA token"| Thanos

    %% Module egress
    ModelReg -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>User Bearer token"| K8sAPI
    GenAI -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>User Bearer token"| K8sAPI
    MaaS -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>User Bearer token"| K8sAPI

